These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, red, aquamarine
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
3. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
5. the person who likes grey is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Color   | red | aquamarine      | grey | ivory |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, yellow, green, fuchsia
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person who likes yellow is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | fuchsia | green | yellow   | purple |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, milk, lemonade
1. the person eating corn is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Beverage   | cola  | lemonade   | milk | coffee    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, jazz, house, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of ambient and the fan of jazz##2
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
5. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | house     | jazz    | d&b       |

