2. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person who likes fuchsia and the thai##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Color           | apricot | red | fuchsia | light-blue |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

