4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating kale is between the person eating lemon and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
5. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
6. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | lemon | kale  | garlic  | avocado   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

