3. the spanish is on the left or right of the australian##3
4. the dutch is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | dutch     | spanish | australian     | french   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

