.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, quad-bike, bus
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pear, potato, tomato
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Transport   | bike | quad-bike | bus   | scooter |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

