.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, folk, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of folk##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | electronic   | folk | trance     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

