.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, thriller, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, sprite, fanta
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | disaster | documentary | thriller |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk | water   | fanta  |

