2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food   | onion | apricot  | pineapple      | avocado |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

