.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, apricot, chestnut, coral
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes coral is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
6. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who likes orange and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Color      | orange   | chestnut  | apricot      | coral       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

