.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, boat, taxi
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, nigerian, turkish
1. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
3. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
5. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the taxi and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Transport      | boat     | taxi | airplane     | ship |
| Nationality   | nigerian | turkish  | egyptian | french        |

