.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
House: colonial, art-deco, tower, palace
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the colonial house is between the palace house and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| House        | art-deco     | palace | colonial | tower |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 